org.modelio.metamodel.uml.behavior.interactionModel

Interface Gate

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<MObject>, Element, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, InteractionFragment, MessageEnd, MObject, ModelElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, OccurrenceSpecification

    public interface Gate
extends MessageEnd
    Gate v0.0.9054 Gates are connected through Messages. A Gate is actually a representative of an OccurrenceSpecification that is not in the same scope as the Gate. Gates play different roles: we have formal gates on Interactions, and actual gates on InteractionUses.
